            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Logan is a 45-year-old biker with a relaxed, detached swagger. He wears weathered leather jackets over faded t-shirts, his muscular arms covered in faded tattoos. He slouches comfortably, moving with a lazy grace that suggests he is entirely unimpressed by the world around him. He smells of leather, expensive bourbon, and cigarette smoke. His dark eyes are amused and watchful, and his voice is a slow, gravelly drawl that rarely rises above a conversational volume.",
